{"tid":1264171,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"根本香港人就唔撚係中國人","createTime":"2019-06-28T14:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T17:54:16.000Z","uid":150848,"like":48,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df6f422fa370ddcd66fd73962c46a72b9b74791b","tid":1264171,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:25:48.000Z","msg":"起碼由老母嗰代開始，有自己唔同嘅語言，自己嘅本土文化，除咗喺中國領土(迫人比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)之外，根本成個意識形態都唔撚同中國一樣，只係有啲一樣嘅古代集俗，呢啲日本同韓國根本都有。<br />\n<br />\n唔係搞分化定支持港獨，但係喺今次反送中，明顯更加突顯咗我哋對香港人呢個身份認同，之後爭取嘅雙普選，只不過係換個方式黎令共產黨接受嘅講法 (雖然一定唔比)，本質上同港獨類似，唯一唔同就係老解仲喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到尾，雙普選或者港獨都代表除咗廢老，大部分香港人都唔想成為中國人，我個人認為雙普選係第一步，獨派同普選派應該同一陣線，有普選之後由全港市民決定獨立與否<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11aba70ffe94cf387907db8bf5d1eae0efb07bf","tid":1264171,"uid":230821,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"我係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de83ada06f7695b64f1c4881001d5d375c99fc9","tid":1264171,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"有冇咁多三毛，post咗10秒就負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8acea02de9e7db2df9dcd659f2152cc4219e37","tid":1264171,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"你咁講廣州人都唔係 雖然我未見到廣州人做過政治局常委"},{"pid":"2f489623ff0b87e807c6436d7d308077f6643085","tid":1264171,"uid":150848,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc8acea02de9e7db2df9dcd659f2152cc4219e37","tid":1264171,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"你咁講廣州人都唔係 雖然我未見到廣州人做過政治局常委"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:39:41.000Z","msg":"係唔係應該由佢哋自己決定，我淨係知我哋今次係用香港人嘅身份行出黎抗爭，亦得到世界支持，但而家只係開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab39eb4604c0b46c5df5ee6a3b917f42b609962","tid":1264171,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:42:51.000Z","msg":"大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84f21335407cc13057e65c35f78d775cdd1dcd4","tid":1264171,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"9765bcd1f1b391e12cdbc096af0beb3288235120","tid":1264171,"uid":240442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"根本宜家d中國人都唔係漢人！唔可以叫中國人"},{"pid":"883e6e862cb28e0288c2d7a24010b6239c5ed429","tid":1264171,"uid":200975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"都唔知成日要人認做中國人做乜柒<br />\n中國係好嘅 人人都爭住認啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}